{"tid":963223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢4千蚊都撚狗無分別甘撚d香港人","createTime":"2018-12-31T12:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T13:38:50.000Z","uid":167451,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62d19aaa7daaf70ed08d66aee78306e370db18d6","tid":963223,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:24:42.000Z","msg":"符合以下資格的人士可申領4000港元：<br />\n<br />\n1) 年滿18歲<br />\n<br />\n2) 持香港身份證，包括新來港人士，但不包括來港工作、求學或接受培訓的香港非永久性居民及其受養人，也不包括以訪客身分來港的人士。<br />\n<br />\n3) 通常居住在香港，包括暫時離開香港而在合理預期情況下會返回香港居住的人士，例如因出差、留學或求醫而離港的香港居民，但不包括已移居海外的人士。<br />\n<br />\n4) 沒有受惠於二零一八至一九年度《財政預算案》就綜合社會保障援助、長者生活津貼、高齡津貼或傷殘津貼發放的額外兩個月款項。<br />\n<br />\n5) 毋須繳交2017/18課稅年度的薪俸稅。<br />\n<br />\n6) 在香港沒有物業。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，任何人士如符合第1至5項資格，但在香港只擁有一所物業作自住用途，而所得的2018至19年度差餉寬減額少於4000港元，可申領4000港元扣除差餉寬減的餘額。任何人士如在香港擁有一所物業而該物業並非用作自住用途，或在香港擁有超過一所物業，不符合計劃的申請資格。<br />\n<br />\n任何人士符合第1項至4項資格，但須繳交2017/18課稅年度的薪俸稅，申領4000港元的情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n1) 如在香港沒有物業，而所得的2017/18課稅年度的薪俸稅稅款寬減額少於4000港元，可申領4000港元扣除薪俸稅稅款寬減額後的餘額；或<br />\n<br />\n2) 如在香港只擁有一所物業作自住用途，而所得的2017/18課稅年度的薪俸稅稅款寬減額和2018至19年度差餉寬減額合計少於4000港元，可申領4000港元扣除差餉寬減及薪俸稅稅款寬減額後的餘額。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B42%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E3%80%80%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%80%E8%B2%BC%E7%9D%87%E6%99%92-071225723.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A24000%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B42%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%2599%2592-071225723.html&d=tEtxbaY%2FktXkIo3bDDTCHaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cb513c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B42%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E3%80%80%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%80%E8%B2%BC%E7%9D%87%E6%99%92-071225723.html</a><br />\n<br />\n1）得果4千蚊！波叔，你知唔知依家d purchasing power 幾低呀？<br />\n2）搞左差不多成年都未拿到，到依家話可以派了，screening processes 有幾多層？<br />\n3）d 學生哥 未滿十八歳既點搞呀？會不會唔好搞甘多程序d handling fees 可以夠埋d 未滿十八歲既學生哥 單呀？"},{"pid":"d44336e729f24abfd6c9c4532409617516a79793","tid":963223,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zbaXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzbaXU.gif&h=f16b6fc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"405e239278dc3565875afc24f5827d5c1cf764e6","tid":963223,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"最好唔派"},{"pid":"6cae9be3e78b0c4d3b442923ef5d1ceb6e62c346","tid":963223,"uid":167451,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"d44336e729f24abfd6c9c4532409617516a79793","tid":963223,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zbaXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzbaXU.gif&h=f16b6fc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"咪撚阻住大家討論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2af7ca72a3e65b4314fbefac94be448ee2f3a8","tid":963223,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6cae9be3e78b0c4d3b442923ef5d1ceb6e62c346","tid":963223,"uid":167451,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"d44336e729f24abfd6c9c4532409617516a79793","tid":963223,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zbaXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzbaXU.gif&h=f16b6fc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"咪撚阻住大家討論啦<img src